source: crates/test-framework/src/snapshot/mod.rs
description: "Query: clickbench_q15"
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: c DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=10                                                                                                              |
|               |   Projection: hits.SearchEngineID, hits.SearchPhrase, count(Int64(1)) AS c                                                                      |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.SearchEngineID, hits.SearchPhrase]], aggr=[[count(Int64(1))]]                                                     |
|               |       BytesProcessedNode                                                                                                                        |
|               |         Filter: CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8View) != Utf8View("")                                                                             |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[SearchEngineID, SearchPhrase], partial_filters=[CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8View) != Utf8View("")]      |
| physical_plan | SortExec: TopK(fetch=10), expr=[c@2 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[false]                                                                        |
|               |   CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                        |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[SearchEngineID@0 as SearchEngineID, SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase, count(Int64(1))@2 as c]                           |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[SearchEngineID@0 as SearchEngineID, SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))]    |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                             |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([SearchEngineID@0, SearchPhrase@1], 16), input_partitions=16                                       |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[SearchEngineID@0 as SearchEngineID, SearchPhrase@1 as SearchPhrase], aggr=[count(Int64(1))]       |
|               |               BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                |
|               |                 CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                     |
|               |                   FilterExec: CAST(SearchPhrase@1 AS Utf8View) !=                                                                               |
|               |                     SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                          |
|               |                       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                     |
|               |                         FallbackOnZeroResultsScanExec                                                                                           |
|               |                           CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                |
|               |                             RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                               |
|               |                               CooperativeExec                                                                                                   |
|               |                                 DuckSqlExec sql= SELECT "SearchEngineID", "SearchPhrase" FROM hits WHERE (CAST(SearchPhrase AS VARCHAR) <> '')  |
|               |                                                                                                                                                 |
